<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930443>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 6–9. 6) Lectotype of Chrysis succincta var. nordstromi Trautmann, 1927 (= Chrysis westerlundi Trautmann, 1927). 7) Lectotype of Chrysis succincta var. chrysoprasina Trautmann, 1927 (= Chrysis illigeri Wesmael, 1839). 8) Holotype of Chrysis scintillans Valkeila, 1971 (= Chrysis solida Haupt, 1957). 9) Lectotype of Chrysis zetterstedti Dahlbom, 1831. Scale 1 mm. Photos: Pekka Malinen (6–8) and Alexander Berg (9)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4930443/files/figure.png" .

